HEADWORD: Byzantinism
<hw>Byzantinism</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>The doctrine that the state is
supreme over the church in ecclesiastical matters.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> Erastianism, Caesaropapism.</syn>⟦br⟧
